snippet.title: SingularityNET
snippet.description:
SingularityNET is the first and only platform that allows AIs to cooperate and coordinate at scale. No longer must AIs exist in silos, only capable of operating within a specific company, infrastructure, or industry.

The future of AI is here. We hope you’ll join us. 

Platform:  https://beta.singularitynet.io
Website:   http://singularitynet.io
on Telegram:  http://t.me/singularitynet
